vernac_cmds: Lemma SumAnglesRec : forall A B C D E : Point, Clockwise A B C -> Clockwise A C D -> Between B A E -> Angle B A C = Angle A C D -> Angle D A E = Angle A D C.
destruct (ExistsCongruentStrictTriangle D A C A D) as (F, (H3, H4)).
apply (SumAngles A B C D F H H0 H4 H2).

Lemma SumAnglesCorollary : forall A B C D E A' B' C' : Point, Clockwise A' B' C' -> Clockwise A B C -> Clockwise A C D -> Angle B A C = Angle A' B' C' -> Angle C A D = Angle B' A' C' -> Between B A E -> Angle D A E = Angle A' C' B'.
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A C A' B') as (B'', (H6, H7)).
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A D A' C') as (C'', (H8, H9)).
assert (H10 : CongruentStrictTriangles A' B' C' A B'' C'').
apply H6; apply ClockwiseBCA; apply H12; autoClockwise.
Lemma TwoEmbeddedTriangles : forall A B C D E : Point, Clockwise A B C -> Between A D B -> Between A E C -> Angle A D E = Angle A B C -> Angle A E D = Angle A C B.
destruct (CentralSymetPoint F A (sym_not_eq (ParallelogrammDistinctCD _ _ _ _ H3))) as (G, (_, H4)).
rewrite <- (SumAnglesRec A F B C G).
rewrite <- (SumAnglesRec A F D E G).
apply ClockwiseBCA; apply (BetweenClockwiseMBC B A F D).
exact (TriangleAMN A B C D E H H0 H1).
Lemma TwoEmbeddedSymTriangles : forall A B C D E : Point, Clockwise A B C -> Between A D B -> Between A E C -> Angle A E D = Angle A C B -> Angle A D E = Angle A B C.
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A C A B) as (B', (H3, H4)).
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A B A C) as (C', (H5, H6)).
assert (H7 := TriangleAMN A B C D E H H0 H1).
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A E A D) as (D', (H8, H9)).
destruct (ExistsHalfLineEquidistant A D A E) as (E', (H10, H11)).
assert (H12 : CongruentStrictTriangles A B C A B' C').
assert (H13 : CongruentStrictTriangles A D E A D' E').
clear H3 H5 H8 H14 H16 H17; generalizeChange.
rewrite H11; rewrite H6; exact (BetweenLSlt _ _ _ H1).
clear H3 H5 H10 H14 H16 H17; generalizeChange.
rewrite H9; rewrite H4; exact (BetweenLSlt _ _ _ H0).
Lemma ExternParallelogramm : forall A B C D E : Point, Parallelogramm A B C D -> Between D C E -> Angle A B C = Angle B C E.
apply sym_eq; apply (SumAnglesRec C D A B E).
Lemma ExternOppParallelogramm : forall A B C D E : Point, Parallelogramm A B C D -> Between B C E -> Angle A B C = Angle D C E.
Lemma ParallelogrammExtern : forall A B C D E : Point, Parallelogramm A B C D -> Clockwise C B E -> Angle A B C = Angle B C E -> Between D C E.
apply (SumAngles C D A B E).
